{"Header 1": "FAQ", "Header 2": "Date-related components locale not working?"}

Ensure correct Day.js locale import:  
```jsx
import dayjs from 'dayjs';
import 'dayjs/locale/zh-cn';
dayjs.locale('zh-cn');
```  
Check for multiple Day.js versions:  
```bash
npm ls dayjs
```  
Ensure version matches [antd’s Day.js dependency](https://github.com/ant-design/ant-design/blob/master/package.json).  
