{"Header 1": "FAQ", "Header 2": "Error using `antd` sub-components with Next.js App Router?"}

Error:
```
Cannot access .Option on the server. You cannot dot into a client module from a server component.
```  
**Workarounds**:  
1. Create wrapper components marked `'use client'`:  
```tsx
'use client';
import { Typography as OriginTypography } from 'antd';

const Title = React.forwardRef<HTMLElement, TitleProps>((props, ref) => (
<OriginTypography.Title ref={ref} {...props} />
));

export { Title };
```  
2. Mark entire page as client-side:  
```tsx
'use client';
// Your component code
```  
Tracking: [Next.js #51593](https://github.com/vercel/next.js/issues/51593)
